VA ASSUMABLE LOAN WITH 4.75% RATE, PURCHASED A LITTLE OVER A YEAR AGO!! 
Great opportunity for VA buyers right now!

This stunning home has been newly updated with luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring, freshly painted walls, brand new LG kitchen appliances, and a new roof! Featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and over 3,300 sq ft, this home features granite countertops, a spacious back yard, extended driveway, an oversized primary suite with vaulted ceiling, and is a great floorplan! Make this your home today! **Please verify if room sizes are important to you**
